WEBVTT

00:03.679 --> 00:05.661
Can you tell me where I can find men's clothes?

00:06.024 --> 00:09.307
Yes, our menswear department is on the second floor.

00:09.573 --> 00:10.037
Thank you.

00:11.539 --> 00:13.973
Excuse me, do you have this shirt in a medium?

00:14.241 --> 00:14.781
Medium?

00:15.078 --> 00:15.969
Let me have a look.

00:16.432 --> 00:20.298
No, I can't seem to find any mediums here on the rack.

00:20.527 --> 00:21.006
Really?

00:21.232 --> 00:22.073
That's too bad. 

00:22.239 --> 00:23.233
I really like it.

00:23.430 --> 00:24.434
I'm really sorry.

00:24.767 --> 00:25.821
Can you check again?

00:25.954 --> 00:27.656
You might have a medium in the stock room.

00:28.023 --> 00:28.832
Good news!

00:29.087 --> 00:30.943
There was exactly one medium left.

00:31.153 --> 00:31.750
Here you go.

00:31.928 --> 00:32.669
Fantastic!

00:32.865 --> 00:33.653
Thanks for your help.

00:33.960 --> 00:34.911
My pleasure, sir.

